question: what keyphrases get most citations ?
query: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(t3.citingpaperid), t1.keyphrasename FROM paperkeyphrase AS t2 JOIN keyphrase AS t1 ON t2.keyphraseid = t1.keyphraseid JOIN cite AS t3 ON t2.paperid = t3.citedpaperid GROUP BY t1.keyphrasename ORDER BY COUNT(t3.citingpaperid) DESC NULLS LAST
